				I heard a rumor that this was originally designed as a teleporter for evil characters.  Verant had decided that it would be too difficult for evil characters to safely travel, so, they put a teleporter room in Neriak linking it to a large number of zones.  <BR>
<BR>
Eventually they decided that evil only teleportation would give evil classes too large an advantage and scrapped the whole system before release.  Then, when Kunark reopened they decided to open up teleportation for everyone through Timorous Deep and they used this as a destination.
